### Notable Campaigns

- **Lightwell HCC onboarding**: Rapid onboarding of Lightwell UI into the HCC platform — 5 tickets covering route theming, navigation simplification, masthead customization, and glass theme integration, all delivered in a very short timeframe ([RHCLOUD-48934](https://redhat.atlassian.net/browse/RHCLOUD-48934), [RHCLOUD-48935](https://redhat.atlassian.net/browse/RHCLOUD-48935), [RHCLOUD-48936](https://redhat.atlassian.net/browse/RHCLOUD-48936), [RHCLOUD-48966](https://redhat.atlassian.net/browse/RHCLOUD-48966), [RHCLOUD-49079](https://redhat.atlassian.net/browse/RHCLOUD-49079))
- **GovCloud CVE remediation**: Batch processing of CVE tickets across multiple repositories, systematically updating vulnerable dependencies
- **Dark mode implementation**: Multi-repo campaign to add PatternFly dark theme support across HCC frontend applications
- **Dependency modernization**: Systematic updates of outdated npm packages, webpack configs, and build tooling
- **Release management**: Automated production release PRs with changelog generation

